#quippartner The new quip toothbrush is here!

🦷quip 360 electric toothbrush:
🪥Fully electric
🪥Holds the ADA Seal of Acceptance 
🪥Oscillating, rotating brush head
🪥9,630 oscillations per minute
🪥Proven to remove up to 11x more plaque
🪥Features 3 brushing intensities for comfort & control
🪥Built-in 2-minute timer with 30-second pulses
🪥Pressure sensor with LED light and vibrations for guidance
🪥Rechargeable with a magnetic USB cable (30-day charge)
🪥Comes with a sleek travel case & countertop stand

🦷Price: $50 (a steal compared to $80+ premium models). Available at getquip.com (there’s a sale happening right now). You can also pick them up at Walmart, Target, and Amazon.

🦷Replacement heads: $8 every three months—or $10 with shipping. Subscribing isn’t required, but if you do subscribe, you’ll save money, earn cash back with their loyalty program, and never forget to replace your heads!

🦷Please note: I only partner with brands I’d recommend to my patients in the op. This one’s a winner for its price point, features, and convenience!
